room_title: Escape room "Escape Plan" by Paranoia Quest in Atlanta
room_address: 3333 Buford Drive NE, Suite VB03, Buford GA 30519
room_description:
You and your friends decided to travel to a third world country as part of a humanitarian aid group. While exploring, you have been arrested in error. Now that you have been locked in a local jail, you have to find a way to contact the US Embassy before anything else goes wrong.
It appears that one of the guards is on your side, and he was able to disconnect the security cameras for you. You have an hour to escape before a new guard arrives and the cameras come back on!
